StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetEnlistedPoolBoardScheduledToShipSummary]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
(@Year int ,@Month int ,@OrgId int )
AS
SELECT [RMNPS] AS RegularMaleNonPriorServiceCount ,[KG] AS MaleReserveGroundCount ,[KA] AS MaleReserveAirCount ,[RFNPS] AS RegularFemaleNonPriorServiceCount ,[KF] AS FemaleReserveGroundAndAirCount ,[PS] AS PriorServiceCount FROM [usmc].[ScheduledToShip] WHERE [FiscalYear] = @Year AND [Month] = @Month AND [Organiza.onId] = @OrgId
